{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"631hw9oh0k8jhc0wlm0joyz","title":"Coding tips","desc":"","updated":1722957682054,"created":1685471254996,"custom":{},"fname":"code","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":".","selfContained":true,"name":"Dendron"},"contentHash":"49ea9ce6393d98d424298bd72d87a214","links":[],"anchors":{"clone-only-the-latest-commit-of-a-git-repository":{"type":"header","text":"Clone only the latest commit of a Git repository","value":"clone-only-the-latest-commit-of-a-git-repository","line":9,"column":0,"depth":1},"source":{"type":"header","text":"Source","value":"source","line":22,"column":0,"depth":2},"edit-git-remote-url":{"type":"header","text":"Edit Git Remote URL","value":"edit-git-remote-url","line":30,"column":0,"depth":1},"django-tests-not-running":{"type":"header","text":"Django tests not running","value":"django-tests-not-running","line":39,"column":0,"depth":1}},"children":["rckztplnjk566zxgkjdtzhl","ziizr10bs55a7fbr3fc61sc","hwyvw05ski3srgkxy31ym7w","1fm4dncuybvd5vqj931b01n","j9wmd96lxohstbdavjirhbo","cfm4n435nhmnbubcoi8a356"],"parent":"root","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"coding-tips\">Coding tips<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#coding-tips\"></a></h1>\n<h1 id=\"clone-only-the-latest-commit-of-a-git-repository\">Clone only the latest commit of a Git repository<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#clone-only-the-latest-commit-of-a-git-repository\"></a></h1>\n<pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">git</span> clone --depth <span class=\"token number\">1</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&#x3C;</span>url<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n</code></pre>\n<p>If you need an specific commit, you can obtain it with the <code>git checkout</code>\ncommand:</p>\n<pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">git</span> checkout <span class=\"token operator\">&#x3C;</span>commit_hash<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n</code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"source\">Source<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#source\"></a></h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Bing AI Chat, 21/9/2023.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://qastack.mx/programming/29368837/copy-a-git-repo-without-history\">Copie un repositorio de git sin historial - QA Stack.</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://es.stackoverflow.com/questions/91014/clonar-repositorio-remoto-de-git-hasta-cierto-commit\">Clonar repositorio remoto de git hasta cierto commit.</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://es.stackoverflow.com/questions/1458/regresar-un-repositorio-a-un-commit-especifico\">Regresar un repositorio a un commit especifico - Stack Overflow.</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.atlassian.com/es/git/tutorials/setting-up-a-repository/git-clone\">Atlassian Git Tutorial.</a></li>\n</ol>\n<h1 id=\"edit-git-remote-url\">Edit Git Remote URL<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#edit-git-remote-url\"></a></h1>\n<pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">git</span> remote set-url origin <span class=\"token operator\">&#x3C;</span>new-url<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n\n</code></pre>\n<p><a href=\"https://chat.openai.com/share/5bbfc058-d6be-4ec8-b03f-be8df3619c37\">Source</a></p>\n<h1 id=\"django-tests-not-running\">Django tests not running<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#django-tests-not-running\"></a></h1>\n<p><strong>Solution.</strong> Make sure you are writing your tests wrapped in classes that inherit from <code>TestCase</code>. Example:</p>\n<pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> django<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>test <span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> TestCase\n\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">FooTest</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>TestCase<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"token function\">setUp</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>self<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">pass</span>\n\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"token function\">tearDown</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>self<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">pass</span>\n\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"token function\">test_this_will</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>self<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">print</span> <span class=\"token string\">'Win'</span>\n</code></pre>\n<p><a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/2037364/django-test-runner-not-finding-tests\">Read more</a></p>\n<hr>\n<strong>Children</strong>\n<ol>\n<li><a href=\"/dendron/notes/cfm4n435nhmnbubcoi8a356\">Code Snippets</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/dendron/notes/1fm4dncuybvd5vqj931b01n\">Coding tips for the R programming language</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/dendron/notes/rckztplnjk566zxgkjdtzhl\">Julia</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/dendron/notes/ziizr10bs55a7fbr3fc61sc\">Power Shell</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/dendron/notes/hwyvw05ski3srgkxy31ym7w\">Python</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/dendron/notes/j9wmd96lxohstbdavjirhbo\">Ruby</a></li>\n</ol>","noteIndex":{"id":"root","title":"Inicio","desc":"","updated":1723094658393,"created":1595961348801,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":".","selfContained":true,"name":"Dendron"},"contentHash":"12b52f465cfc40b05a6f542f8379206b","links":[],"anchors":{},"children":["631hw9oh0k8jhc0wlm0joyz","rzreoc67l24hzknyqbn3a9b"],"parent":null,"data":{},"body":"\n"},"collec